            Gabby Mishler
          
          
            
              I am a first-year statistics major at Bucknell
              University! I grew up in a small town in Bedford County,
              PA, where I have the most caring, supportive friends and
              family. It is hard to be away from them, but I know so
              many incredible opportunities lie ahead! My dream job is
              to work in the analytics department of an NHL team, and
              this course has brought me one step closer to it. Welcome
              to my MATH 230 journey!
